'''Ad. Bobonaro''' or '''Associação Desportiva Bobonaro''' is a football club of [[East Timor]] from [[Bobonaro]]. The team plays in the [[Taça Digicel]].<ref>[http://andy1890.wordpress.com/2011/03/09/adidas-and-taca-digicel-kit-deal-until-2021/ Adidas and TAÇA Digicel, Kit deal until 2021]</ref>
