'''Hong Kong Schools Sports Federation football team''' was a football team established by [[Hong Kong Schools Sports Federation]] and formed by students from [[Hong Kong]] secondary schools. They were last competing in [[Hong Kong Third District Division League]] before it dissolved in the 2011–12 season.
