'''St. John's Sports Club''' is a [[Grenada|Grenadian]] football club from [[Gouyave]], [[Saint John Parish, Grenada|Saint John Parish]] that plays in the [[Grenada League|Grenada Premier Division]]. <ref name="GFAPL">{{cite web|last1=Stokkermans|first1=Karel|title=Grenada 2015|url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesg/grenada2015.html#prem|website=Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation|publisher=RSSSF.com|accessdate=12 May 2016|date=10 January 2016}}</ref>

