'''Stian Bogar''' (born 10 November 1976) is a Norwegian [[Shooting sports|sport shooter]].

He participated at the [[2018 ISSF World Shooting Championships]], winning a medal.<ref>[https://www.issf-sports.org/media/resultspdf/2018/1750/I100000IA0509180900.1.FR60PR.0.001.pdf 50 m rifle prone results]</ref>

